# This directory is the inbox for new community templates.
#
# Drop a `.nyxtemplate` file here in a pull request. CI will:
#   1. Lint it (schema, variables, secrets, cover validity).
#   2. Unpack it into `community/templates/<slug>/` (template.json + cover + meta.yml).
#   3. Delete the original file from this directory.
#   4. Push the unpacked form back into your PR.
#
# See ../CONTRIBUTING.md for full instructions.
